name: Wingur
tagline: The ultimative openSource Imgur Client for Windows Plattforms
body:
### What is Wingur
Wingur is an openSource [Imgur](http://imgur.com/) Client for Windows Plattforms.
For you who are not familiar with Imgur it's a website with the most viral images on the net.

***
### Join Us
You can join us (or me) with this project if you're interested, just click the link in the header.
